      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a good start, love the 'scabbed wounds' thing. it's very atmospheric. to really make it feel real for the audience, i want to flesh out the people in this area. can you describe some of the types of people you'd see hanging out on these corners or loitering in those alleyways? i want to capture the specific vibe of the crowd that makes someone feel unwelcome or threatened. just some brief character sketches to help me visualize the tension.",
